def is_pants(pants:item):
    # Determine if the item is pants
    symbol pants_is=is_clothes_pants(pants)
    return pants_is

behavior approach_pants(pants:item):
    body:
        achieve close_char(char, pants)
        # Move the character close to the pants

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        # Check all items in the scene to identify pants
        foreach pants: item:
            if is_pants(pants) and not visited(pants):
                observe(pants, "Check is there pants")

        # Move close to the located pants
        if exists pants: item : is_pants(pants) and visited(pants):
            bind pants: item where:
                is_pants(pants) and visited(pants)
            approach_pants(pants)
